# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SmileShift Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── REQUIRED (All Free) ─────────────────────────────

# Supabase (FREE tier: 500MB DB, 1GB storage, 50K MAU)
# Sign up at https://supabase.com → Create project → Get these from Settings > API
PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here

# App Config (no signup needed)
PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173
PUBLIC_APP_NAME=SmileShift

# ─── REQUIRED FOR PAYMENTS (Free until transactions) ─

# Stripe (FREE to create account, test mode is 100% free)
# Sign up at https://stripe.com → Developers → API keys
# Use test keys (pk_test_ / sk_test_) for development — no real money
PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your-key-here
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_your-key-here
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_your-secret-here

# ─── NO API KEY NEEDED ───────────────────────────────

# Maps: We use Leaflet + OpenStreetMap (100% free, no API key!)
# Geocoding: We use Nominatim (free, no key) or Supabase PostGIS

# AI/Matching: All matching logic runs in PostgreSQL (no external AI API)
# Smart scoring, geo-proximity, and ranking are pure SQL functions

# ─── OPTIONAL (Only if you want these features) ──────

# Sentry error tracking (FREE tier: 5K errors/month)
# Sign up at https://sentry.io — or skip and use Vercel's built-in error logs
# SENTRY_DSN=
# SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=

# Upstash Redis (FREE tier: 10K commands/day)
# Only needed at scale for rate limiting & caching
# Sign up at https://upstash.com
# UPSTASH_REDIS_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_TOKEN=
